title: Annuar confirms running for FAM post, to lock horns with crown prince
text:
More 
Umno information chief Annuar Musa has confirmed that he would contest for the Football Association of Malaysia (FAM) president post. 
In a Facebook posting, Annuar said he has submitted a letter accepting his nomination to FAM secretary-general Hamidin Mohd Amin.
